snippet.title: Winged Knights Penetration Gameplay (1080p HD / 60FPS)
snippet.description:
Winged Knights : Penetration is an arcade style flying competition between the feuding knights of future! Currently three different levels of opponents are in game, randomly placed barriers, local co-op or versus is up to you!
